&lt;p&gt;We’re looking for an experienced Director of Product Management to lead consumer growth and engagement strategy at ClassPass. You’ll oversee the vision and execution, lead a team of PMs and partner closely with cross-functional stakeholders.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This role is a good fit if you…&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Have built and scaled consumer products during a hyper-growth stage&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Can define a product vision that inspires and drives clarity for a team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Are execution-focused and know how to unblock teams while balancing speed and quality&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as a true product owner with a high bar for craft and detail&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bring strong business acumen to decision making, weighing business impact and making tough trade-offs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Have a track record for incorporating experimentation into your build process; know how to construct an effective test and analyze the results&lt;/li&gt;
