&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2+ years of full-cycle B2B sales or account management experience, including field sales&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Consistent track record of hitting or exceeding quota and performance goals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong negotiation skills with a solutions-first approach&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deep knowledge of your regional fitness and wellness market, with active professional connections&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Confidence navigating both cold outreach and warm relationship-building across channels&lt;/li&gt;
